fulltitle: An IAJE Clinic in Playing Free Jazz with Kenny Werner
description: In this clip from www.artistshousemusic.org - Jazz piano great Kenny Werner gives a free jazz clinic sponsored by the International Association of Jazz Education. He discusses the history of free music, what it is and what it means, and offers extended thoughts on what players can and should to do prepare themselves mentally, physically, and musically for the unique challenges that free music presents. He also offers working demonstrations of his lectures through free-music performances of several jazz standards.
